                "invention-title": [
                    "New energy and flue CO2 recovery-based waste salt harmless alkali production method",
                    "基于新能源和回收烟道CO2的废盐无害化制碱方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a waste salt harmless alkali production method based on new energy and flue CO2 recovery, and belongs to the technical field of new energy coupling resource recycling. The method comprises the following steps: capturing and collecting carbon dioxide from flue gas, electrolyzing water by using electric energy obtained by new energy power generation to prepare hydrogen, pressurizing and catalyzing the prepared hydrogen and nitrogen to produce green ammonia, and harmlessly preparing green soda ash and ammonium chloride products by using the carbon dioxide and the green ammonia as raw materials and industrial sodium chloride waste salt. The device is scientific and reasonable in design, green new energy such as wind power, photovoltaic energy and photo-thermal energy is used for generating electricity and electrolyzing water to produce hydrogen, the hydrogen and nitrogen separated from air are pressurized and catalyzed to produce green ammonia, and carbon dioxide is captured from flue gas by adopting membrane separation, a chemical solvent absorption method or a pressure swing adsorption method; the green ammonia and the carbon dioxide are used as raw materials to produce sodium carbonate and ammonium chloride together with industrial waste salt, so that resource recycling is realized, and carbon emission can be effectively reduced while green low-carbon sodium carbonate production is carried out."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了基于新能源和回收烟道CO2的废盐无害化制碱方法，属于新能源耦合资源循环利用的技术领域。本发明的方法为从烟道气中捕获收集二氧化碳，以新能源发电所得电能电解水制氢气并将所制氢气与氮气加压催化生产绿氨，将上述二氧化碳和绿氨为原料与工业氯化钠废盐无害化制备绿色纯碱和氯化铵产品。本发明设计科学合理，以风电、光伏和光热等绿色新能源发电电解水制氢，与从空气中分离出的氮气加压催化生产绿氨，采用膜分离、化学溶剂吸收法或变压吸附法从烟道气中捕集二氧化碳，以上述绿氨和二氧化碳为原料与工业废盐生产纯碱和氯化铵，实现资源循环利用，进行绿色低碳纯碱生产的同时还能有效降低碳排放。"
                }
            ]
